body: "# Capability: Security & code scanning (living backlog)\n\nOwns repository security posture work that previously had no capability home:\n- Semgrep Code finding triage batches (first import: pm-oz8u, 40 findings from 2026-07-06 CSV — 6 High spawn-shell-true, 34 Medium prototype-pollution/non-literal-RegExp/dependabot-cooldown).\n- Dependabot dependency hygiene (pm-2czc closed the 2026-07-06 unblock: @types/node 26, pnpm cooldown, codeql-action lockstep group).\n- Secret guardrails and history-redact usage policy (see 2026-05-22 history-repair learning: never quote secret-pattern literals into pm text).\n- Future CodeQL / scanner integrations.\n\nConvention: each scanner import creates one batch Task parented here, with one Issue per platform finding (Semgrep ID as issue code) so findings stay individually triageable. Sibling epic pm-92if owns CodeFactor (maintainability) findings; this epic owns security-class findings."
